---
title: Zucchini, Chicken and Lemon Linguine with Basil Pesto and Goat Cheese
description: We love zucchini all year long and this dish combines some of our favourite flavours: sweet bell peppers, zucchini, chicken and basil pesto! A little squeeze of lemon at the end brings the whole dish together!
